                <mxCell id="g4n" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Symptom&lt;/b&gt;: stats wrong across devices; learned list reverts&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Files&lt;/b&gt;: learnedCharacters, studyStatsFirestore, profileLocalStats, merge on login&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Flow&lt;/b&gt;: local write → debounced sync; login mergeLearnedOnLogin&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;State&lt;/b&gt;: localStorage + users/{uid}/characters|stats|studyDays&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Root&lt;/b&gt;: mergeLearnedLists rating max; recordStudyActivity only if signed in&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tests&lt;/b&gt;: none — manual multi-device QA&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#9673a6;spacingLeft=10;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fontSize=14;" parent="g4" vertex="1">
