                <mxCell id="g5n" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Symptom&lt;/b&gt;: audio 404; player stuck; images missing in reading&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Files&lt;/b&gt;: ExamRunner, imagePath.js, exam/data/H11329.js, public/exams/&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Flow&lt;/b&gt;: exam.audio[key] → /exams/{id}/audio/{file}&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;State&lt;/b&gt;: exam JS module; answers in Firestore examAttempts&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Root&lt;/b&gt;: assets not in repo/build; path rewrite on hosting&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tests&lt;/b&gt;: manual Exam tab; verify public/exams in deploy&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;spacingLeft=10;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fontSize=14;" parent="g5" vertex="1">
